Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说说话啊 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
